---
import MainLayout from "../layout/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Alexander About"
  seoTitle="About Alexander, Software Engineer"
  seoDesc={`Hi there! My name is Alexander, and I'm a software engineer with over 2 years of experience`}
>
  <div class="w-6/12 mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-5xl">About</h1>
    <img
      src="images/IconAlex.jpg"
      class="my-2 shadow-md drop-shadow-[10px_10px_35px_rgba(39,245,131,0.6)]"
    />
    <p>
      Hi there! My name is Alexander, and I'm a software engineer with over 2
      years of experience in the industry. I'm passionate about building
      high-quality software that solves real-world problems and makes people's
      lives easier.
    </p>
    <p>
      My expertise lies in full-stack development and game development, with a focus on web and game development. I have a strong foundation in both languages and tools for building applications. I'm proficient in a variety of programming languages, including JavaScript and C#. I'm comfortable working with tools and frameworks like Node.js.
    </p>
    <p>
      In addition to my technical skills, I pride myself on my ability to collaborate with team members and communicate effectively with stakeholders. I'm a natural problem solver and enjoy tackling complex challenges.
    </p>
    <p>
      When I'm not coding, you can find me hiking in the mountains or playing guitar in my local band. I'm always looking for new opportunities to work on exciting projects, so if you're interested in collaborating, please feel free to get in touch. Thanks for stopping by!
    </p>
  </div>
</MainLayout>

